INSERT INTO quarterbacks VALUES('54','Andy Dalton','Cowboys','QB','17.0','28.0','197.0','1.0','1.0','1.0','2.0','0.0','Dalton signed with Dallas as Dak Prescott''s backup after being released by the Bengals. Last season, Dalton appeared in 13 games and racked up 20 total touchdowns to go along with 14 interceptions. He posted his worst YPA (6.6) and completion rate (59%) since his rookie season in 2011. He managed one weekly fantasy finish better than 10th and hasn''t finished a season better than 12th in fantasy points since 2013. He''s only worth considering for an add if Prescott goes down with an injury.');
