INSERT INTO quarterbacks VALUES('94','Jacob Eason','Colts','QB','','','','','','','','','The Colts selected Jacob Eason in the fourth round of April''s draft. Eason has drawn comparisons to Carson Palmer and Brock Osweiler due to his huge frame (6-foot-6, 231 pounds) and very strong arm. That''s enough to make Eason an attractive developmental prospect, but the former Huskie lacks mobility and will need to overcome major struggles while dealing with pressure. Eason was dramatically better at Washington last season than he was at Georgia in 2016, which adds optimism to his trajectory. He''ll have plenty of time to learn behind Philip Rivers and Jacoby Brissett.');
