INSERT INTO quarterbacks VALUES('99','Jake Fromm','Bills','QB','','','','','','','','','The Bills selected Fromm with a fifth-round pick in April''s draft. Fromm has the look of a game manager in the pros. He''s a good decision-maker and does an excellent job avoiding negative plays (18 interceptions, 51 sacks, nine fumbles in 43 games at Georgia), but he adds the bare minimum with his legs (40 career rushing yards, 5.01 40-yard dash) and completed only 61% of his passes last season. He''s also on the small side (6-foot-2, 219 pounds), with shaky accuracy and an underwhelming arm. Fromm will spend his first few NFL seasons learning the ropes behind Josh Allen.');
