INSERT INTO wide_receivers VALUES('186','James Proche','Ravens','WR','1.0','18.0','0.0','0.0','0.0','0.0','Baltimore selected Proche in the sixth round of April''s draft. Proche is on the small side (5-foot-11, 201 pounds) and isn''t particularly fast or quick, but he still managed big-time numbers at SMU, thanks to excellent ball skills, hands and production in contested situations. Proche''s rate stats weren''t great in 2019 (7.2 YPT, 4.1 RAC), but his 2.6 YPRR was solid and his 111 receptions tied for most in the FBS. Proche will look to carve out a role as a slot receiver and returner but is unlikely to find his way to fantasy value in 2020.');
