INSERT INTO tight_ends VALUES('87','Adam Trautman','Saints','TE','4.0','42.0','0.0','0.0','0.0','0.0','The Saints traded up to select Trautman in the third round of April''s draft. Trautman has terrific size (6-foot-5, 255 pounds) and is a capable blocker with good hands (two drops last season) and post-catch ability. He showed well at both the Senior Bowl and combine (his 6.78 three cone was best among tight ends). Granted, it was lesser competition, but Trautman put up huge numbers at Dayton with 110 catches for 1,511 yards and 23 touchdowns during the past two seasons. He''ll warm the bench behind Jared Cook and Josh Hill in the short term but has the chops to push for fantasy relevance in a year or two.');
