INSERT INTO tight_ends VALUES('95','Brycen Hopkins','Rams','TE','4.0','41.0','0.0','0.0','0.0','0.0','The Rams selected Hopkins in the fourth round of April''s draft. The Purdue product has terrific speed and is a good athlete, route runner and has vertical presence, which provides him big upside as a pure pass-catching tight end. On the other hand, he''s not an option as a blocker and has significant drop concerns. Hopkins put up big raw numbers last season (61-830-7), but dropped nine of his 93 targets. Hopkins has drawn comps to Evan Engram and Jared Cook, which are a pretty good indicator of his fantasy potential. He''ll learn the ropes behind Tyler Higbee and Gerald Everett in 2020.');
