INSERT INTO tight_ends VALUES('103','Albert Okwuegbunam','Broncos','TE','3.0','34.0','0.0','0.0','0.0','0.0','Okwuegbunam was reunited with college quarterback Drew Lock when Denver selected him in the fourth round of April''s draft. A favorite target of Lock''s during his best collegiate season in 2018, the Missouri tight end saw his production drop off without him in 2019. Okwuegbunam has terrific size (6-foot-5, 258 pounds) and speed (he ran position-best 4.49 40-yard dash) but isn''t much of a blocker and has struggled with drops (he dropped a class-high 15% of his 47 targets last season). Fantasy value is a long way off for a tight end buried behind Noah Fant.');
